<li id="cite_note-Comput_Educ-23"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Comput_Educ_23-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFC._Chou_and_M.C._Hsiao2002">C. Chou and M.C. Hsiao (2002). "Internet addiction, usage, gratification, and pleasure experience: the Taiwan college students' case". <i>Comput Educ 35 (2000)</i>: pp. 65–80.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Internet+addiction%2C+usage%2C+gratification%2C+and+pleasure+experience%3A+the+Taiwan+college+students%27+case&amp;rft.jtitle=Comput+Educ+35+%282000%29&amp;rft.aulast=C.+Chou+and+M.C.+Hsiao&amp;rft.au=C.+Chou+and+M.C.+Hsiao&amp;rft.date=2002&amp;rft.pages=pp.+65%E2%80%9380&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Internet_addiction_disorder"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-Wu-24"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Wu_24-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFH.R._Wu_and_K.J._Zhu2004">H.R. Wu and K.J. Zhu (2004). "Path analysis on related factors causing Internet addiction disorder in college students". <i>Chin J Public Health 20</i>: pp. 1363–1364.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Path+analysis+on+related+factors+causing+Internet+addiction+disorder+in+college+students&amp;rft.jtitle=Chin+J+Public+Health+20&amp;rft.aulast=H.R.+Wu+and+K.J.+Zhu&amp;rft.au=H.R.+Wu+and+K.J.+Zhu&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft.pages=pp.+1363%E2%80%931364&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Internet_addiction_disorder"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
